Additional Terms:

1. Circular Economy Requirement
   This software may only be used for circular economy applications that facilitate
   the sharing, repurposing, or more efficient use of resources within communities.
   Any derivative work must maintain this focus on resource circulation and
   community benefit.

2. Attribution Requirements
   In addition to the standard CC BY-NC 4.0 attribution requirements, any project
   using this code must:

   - Maintain a visible link to https://www.peels.app in their application
   - Include a reference to the original Peels project in their documentation
   - Preserve all existing copyright notices and attributions

3. Database Schema Protection
   While the code is freely available under this license, the database schema
   and structure remain protected by copyright. You may use and modify the schema
   for your own circular economy project, but you may not use it for any other
   purpose without explicit permission.

